c: 2
v: 143
t: "Ko wano nii Men wa…óiri on mofte hakindii…óe fii yo on laato seedoytoo…ìe e dow yim…ìe …ìen, Nulaa…óo on seeditoyoo e dow mo'on. Men wa…óiraa oo Qibla mo fewtataa e mu'un si wanaa no Men anndira on jokkoowo Nulaa…óo on e on ruttotoo…óo batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii …óum laatike ko sattu-…óum, si wanaa e dow …ìen …ìe Allah fewni. Allah Laatoraali yeeboowo liimanaaku mo'on: Pellet, Allah ko Hilnotoo…óo yim…ìe …ìen Yurmee …ìe"